## ğŸ’» Usage

### â–¶ï¸ Run the Streamlit App

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

---

### ğŸ§ª Interact with the System

1. Open the app in your browser at **[http://localhost:8501](http://localhost:8501)**
2. Upload a PDF document using the file uploader
3. Wait for the **â€œDocument processed successfully!â€** message
4. Enter your question in the text input field
5. View the generated answer
6. Expand the **ğŸ“Œ Source Chunks** section to see the supporting document text

---

## âš™ï¸ Core Technology Stack

| Component     | Library / Model                                     | Role              |
| ------------- | --------------------------------------------------- | ----------------- |
| Frontend      | `streamlit`                                         | Web interface     |
| LLM           | `ChatGoogleGenerativeAI (gemini-2.5-flash)`         | Answer generation |
| Embeddings    | `GoogleGenerativeAIEmbeddings (text-embedding-004)` | Text to vectors   |
| Vector Store  | `FAISS`                                             | Similarity search |
| Orchestration | `RetrievalQA`                                       | RAG workflow      |
| Text Splitter | `RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter`                    | PDF chunking      |

---

## ğŸ¨ Custom Theme (Optional)

